remarks.format: ## Remarks A profile is a subset of the full .NET Framework. For example, the .NET Framework Client Profile is a subset of the .NET Framework 3.5 Service Pack 1, and the .NET Framework 4 Client Profile is a subset of the .NET Framework 4.5. For more information, see [.NET Framework Client Profile](/dotnet/framework/deployment/client-profile).
